'''第26届评论家选择电影奖'''（{{lang-en|26th Critics' Choice Awards}}）于2021年3月7日在美国[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]{{le|圣莫妮卡机场|Santa Monica Airport}}贝克机库（{{lang|en|Barker Hangar}}）举行，与{{le|第11届评论家选择电视奖|11th Critics' Choice Television Awards}}同期举办，表彰[[2020年电影|2020年电影行业]]杰出成绩。典礼由[[CW电视网|CW电视网]]转播，[[泰·迪哥斯|泰·迪哥斯]]第三次主持<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.criticschoice.com/2020/06/annual-critics-choice-awards-returns-to-the-cw-network-on-sunday-march-7-2021-with-host-taye-diggs/ |title=Annual Critics Choice Awards Returns To The CW Network On Sunday, March 7, 2021 With Host Taye Diggs |date=2020-06-20 |publisher=[[Critics_Choice_Association|Critics Choice Association]] |access-date=2020-06-20}}</ref>。提名名单于2021年2月8日公布<ref>{{cite web |url=http://criticschoice.com/2021/02/film-nominations-announced-for-the-26th-annual-critics-choice-awards/ |title=Film nominees for the 26th annual Critics Choice Awards have been announced |date=2021-02-08 |publisher=[[Critics_Choice_Association|Critics Choice Association]] |access-date=2021-02-08}}</ref>。

